    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, this car is an absolute dream. It\u2019s been totally babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or a speck of dust anywhere! It drives like a cloud and I\u2019m only letting it go because I need something bigger for the family. You won\u2019t find another one in this kind of shape. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
