    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing my pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single mark on it. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43900.0,
