      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision. The S54 inline-six engine delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure optimal camshaft timing. The chassis is structurally reinforced at the rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for razor-sharp turn-in. Power is managed by a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to factory tolerances, ensuring this high-revving icon performs exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
